<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="medium-n">medium <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'miːdiəm/    美 /'miːdiəm/  </p>
<p>[C] (pl media / mediums)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>媒质；媒介物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sound travels through the medium of air. 
声音通过空气这一媒介传播。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>新闻媒体；传媒</strong></h4>
<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>手段；工具：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Television can be an excellent <strong>medium for</strong> education.
电视会是一种绝好的教育手段。</p></div></div>